Package org.mapsforge.android.maps.overlay

Class Summary
ArrayCircleOverlay ArrayCircleOverlay is a thread-safe implementation of the CircleOverlay class using an ArrayList as internal data structure.
ArrayItemizedOverlay ArrayItemizedOverlay is a thread-safe implementation of the ItemizedOverlay class using an ArrayList as internal data structure.
ArrayWayOverlay ArrayWayOverlay is a thread-safe implementation of the WayOverlay class using an ArrayList as internal data structure.
CircleOverlay<Circle extends OverlayCircle> CircleOverlay is an abstract base class to display OverlayCircles.
ItemizedOverlay<Item extends OverlayItem> ItemizedOverlay is an abstract base class to display OverlayItems.
Overlay Overlay is the abstract base class for all types of overlays.
OverlayCircle OverlayCircle holds all parameters of a single circle on a CircleOverlay.
OverlayItem OverlayItem holds all parameters of a single element on an ItemizedOverlay, such as position, marker, title and textual description.
OverlayList An OverlayList manages the overlay list of a MapView.
OverlayWay OverlayWay holds all parameters of a single way on a WayOverlay.
WayOverlay<Way extends OverlayWay> WayOverlay is an abstract base class to display OverlayWays.
 

Enum Summary
Overlay.EventType Enumeration of all types of events.
